Title: Why Me?
---
Have you heard about the king
who accompanied each soldier,
new recruit, onto the field
to surprise him, attacking him,
testing his mettle for battle?
That king was once nearly killed
by a servant who fought back,
and that servant, the king held
in highest esteem.
